OL,5, Former president Donald Trump reported 
OL,6, steep business losses in his final year
OL,7, in the White House, allowing the       
OL,8, billionaire to avoid paying income tax.
OL,10,FHe also did not face tax audits during 
OL,11,Fhis first two years in office, despite 
OL,12,Frules requiring the review of tax      
OL,13,Ffilings by sitting presidents.         
OL,15,FThe revelations came after Democrats   
OL,16,Fvoted to release the records on Tuesday
OL,17,Fafter a four-year legal battle.        
OL,19,FA spokesman for Mr Trump said the      
OL,20,Frelease was politically motivated.     
